ence, after which\ndissipation becomes dominant and the electrons start to subtract energy from\nthe magnetic field and dissipate it via the pressure-strain interaction at\nsub-ion scales.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Dec 2021 18:17:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 26 Jul 2022 12:55:49 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 11 Oct 2022 12:14:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-30"}
