es. The\nautomatic processing of requirements involves the extraction of sentences\ncontaining terms identified as relevant to a requirement. The identified\nrequirement is then indexed and stored in a representation that can be used for\nquery processing.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Dec 2021 15:37:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-28"}
